        "57037": {
          "vnum": 57037,
          "name": "Shadowed Woods",
          "description": "The dark woods seem to grow darker as you approach the heart of the forest. The trees branch high above, but vines hang down from them to just above your head, and the brush reaches up to your waist from below. You can forge your toward the center to the east, head to the river to the south, or along the hill to the west. A shadow flickers off to your right.",
