          "vnum": 57039,
          "name": "The Dark Forest",
          "description": "Around you the forest screams silently. Beneath you it coils patiently, winding slowly up and around until it strangles the very air. Thick trunks crowd close together and block you at every step. To the south, a wall of thorny vines offers to bring you to a bloody end. You can flee north or east.",
