        "57040": {
          "vnum": 57040,
          "name": "The Edge of Night",
          "description": "Huge trunks soar gracefully upward, then spread their branches and close out the sky. You stand in utter blackness amidst the pale but flourishing undergrowth. Insects abound, thickening the air in cloud-like swarms. Above all, there is silence. Not a sound reaches your ears through the moist air, that you at times forget you are moving. North and south, the forest thins. West of here lies the heart of the dark woods.",
