        "57041": {
          "vnum": 57041,
          "name": "A Small Clearing in the Forest",
          "description": "Here among the ash trees you find a small circle of bare earth, in the center of which stands a small hut. As you enter the clearing, you feel a wave of calm wash over you, as if the area were blessed against evil. The tracks of a bear in the soil remind you, though, that not all things harmful are evil. A path leads north out of the clearing.",
