        "57042": {
          "vnum": 57042,
          "name": "Edge of the Forest",
          "description": "The forest seems to be expanding slowly over the grasslands, sending out saplings like those which now surround you to scout the borders. The wide spacing makes for easy travel between the trees, and the undergrowth consists primarily of the grasses that cover the slopes to the east. A stand of ash is visible to the south, and a path leads into the denser trees to the west. To the east, the trees end.",
